at 00:00, 08:00, and 16:00 UTC using the time-weighted average premium between perpetual and spot prices. Funding payments are exchanged between long and short positions based on market sentiment, with rates typically ranging from -0.01% to 0.375% per cycle. The exchange's zero maker fee policy allows traders to capture funding payments while maintaining positions at minimal cost through limit orders."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
